article_id:261,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding a Display Issue in the Void Battles Top Menu Screen,image_path:,message:<div>We have found an issue in the newly added Void Battles&#39; top menu screen, where the &quot;Daily Bonus&quot; and &quot;Double Rewards&quot; icons will be displayed for users who have purchased the &quot;7-Day Pack (Double Bonus)&quot; from the shop.</div><div><br></div><div>Please note that even if these icons are displayed, the rewards from the Void Battles will not be doubled. Additionally, there is no Daily Bonus for the Void Battles.</div><div><br></div><div>We are currently investigating this issue. Any further updates will be added to this notice.<br><br><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1550835000"></span>]</strong></span><br>The above issue has been fixed by the data update that took place at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1550835000"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1550818200,update_time1550835188